{"id":897152,"date":[{"year":1993,"month":2,"day":2}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"国际新闻·体育新闻","special_issue":"","column":"迎东亚运英语100句","genre":"","count":"283","ytitle":"","mtitle":"AT　THE　 AIRPORT　在机场","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"2.INTRODUCTION　NICE TO MEET YOU"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"介绍见到你真高兴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Wang: Mr.Lee, may I introduce you to Mr.Liu?Mr.Liu, this is Mr.Lee."},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王李先生，请允许我把你介绍给刘先生。刘先生这位是李先生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Lee:Nice to meet you."},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李见到你真高兴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Liu: Nice to meet you, too. My name is LIUBaifa. Welcome to Shanghai."},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘我也是。我叫刘百发。欢迎到上海来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Lee: Thank you, Mr.Liu."},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李谢谢，刘先生。"}]}